<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>FoodLink</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/FoodLink.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body>
    <header class="header">
        <div id="logo">
            <img src="/images/Logo.png">
        </div>
        <div>
            <p id="title">FoodLink:</p>
            <p id="subtitle">Every Meal Matters!</p>
        </div>
        <div id="login">
            <form action="/action">
                <h3 id="ngo">For NGO's</h3>
                <label for="loginbtn"></label>
                <button id="loginbtn">Login</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="msg1">
        <div id="msg1title">
            Join the Fight Against Hunger with Our New Initiative
        </div>
        <div id="msg1para">
            In India yearly ,377 Millions people go hungry, while 2 Lakh tones of perfectly good food goes to waste. Our
            platform is here to change that. By connecting individuals, hotels, mess halls, and event organizers with
            NGOs and local charities, we ensure surplus food reaches those who need it most instead of ending up in the
            trash.
            <br>
            Whether it's leftover food from a celebration, excess from a hotel kitchen, or unserved meals at a community
            event, you can make a difference. Simply share details of the surplus food on our platform, and we'll ensure
            it gets to the right hands swiftly and safely.
            <br>
            Together, we can reduce food waste and bring hope to those who need it most. Your small step can create a
            big impact. Let's ensure no one goes to bed hungryâ€”join us in this meaningful mission today!
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="information">
        <div id="aboutus">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <P>"Food Link bridges the gap between food surplus and hunger. We connect donors with NGOs to ensure no meal
                goes to waste. Join us in creating a world where everyone gets to eat."</P>
            <label for="aboutusbtn"></label>
            <button id="aboutusbtn"> Know More >></button>
        </div>
        <div id="register">
            <h2>Reduce Wastage</h2>
            <p>"Millions of meals go to waste every day. Register your NGO to receive surplus food and help fight hunger
                while reducing waste."</p>
            <label for="registerbtn"></label>
            <button id="registerbtn"> Register >> </button>
        </div>
        <div id="donateus">
            <h2>Donate Us</h2>
            <p>"Your support helps us fight hunger, reduce food waste, and reach more people in need. Donate food or
                funds today to make a lasting impact!"</p>
            <label for="donateusbtn"></label>
            <button id="donateusbtn"> Donate >> </button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="msg2">
        <div id="msg2title">
            Why Should You Donate to our NGO for Food Drives?
        </div>
        <div id="msg2para">
            Donating food to people in need is a small but crucial task in the fight against hunger and malnutrition.
            Millions of people face food shortages daily, which makes it impossible to get the proper nutrition that is
            required to live a healthy life. Food donation drives bring proper meals to the underprivileged who cannot
            afford them or are unable to access them otherwise. A donation for food, in any form, also brings a sense of
            satisfaction when you realize that today, you are the reason behind someone's smile. If you feel that you
            are ready to spread some joy and wish to give back to society. You can explore our website for our food
            donation campaigns.
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="statistics" >
        <div>
            <h2 id="sttitle">Food & Fund Statistics</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="number">
            <div id="food">
                <h3>Accepted Food Donations:</h3>
                <h2 style="color: #f60;">
                    <%= accepteddonations.length %>
                </h2>
            </div>
            <div id="money">
                <h3> Total Funds Collected:</h3>
                <h2 style="color: #f60;">&#8377;12586</h2>
            </div>
            <div id="pending">
                <h3>Available Food Donations:</h3>
                <h2 style="color: #f60;">
                    <%= availabledonations.length %>
                </h2>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="Footer">
        <div id="address">
            <h3>Address</h3>
            <p>Survey No. 27, Near Trimurti Chowk</p>
            <P>Dhankwadi, Pune - 411043</P>
            <p><i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i> +91 20 24371101 </p>
            <p>
                <i class="fa-solid fa-map-location"></i>
                <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/2JNF3bfGsngKYw6B7" id="gmap">Google Map</a>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div id="Contact">
